arguments.command:
curl -s -X POST http://rec-agent-api:8000/v1/messages \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "domain": "movie",
    "message": "Good day. I am hoping you might assist me in locating a film worth my time. I should say at the outset that I have spent the better part of my working life in comparative literature and education, and so I find myself quite drawn to cinema that engages seriously with narrative craft, cultural complexity, or the literary tradition — adaptations of novels, films built around moral or philosophical questions, that sort of thing. I am not terribly interested in spectacle for its own sake. Could you perhaps begin by asking me a few questions so that we may narrow down what might suit me?"
  }' | jq '.'

